too insane to be true.

639
00:50:07,582 --> 00:50:09,085
FISHERMAN: Aah.

640
00:50:09,118 --> 00:50:10,552
MARIE: Where are we going?

641
00:50:10,585 --> 00:50:11,854
FISHERMAN: Listen,
the tourist season

642
00:50:11,888 --> 00:50:13,455
